# Layered Architecture (rule cứng)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[app/api/v1/*<br/>HTTP layer — route handlers]
    S[app/services/*<br/>Business logic — gpa_calculator, warning_engine, import_service, ...]
    M[app/models/*<br/>SQLAlchemy ORM — 10 bảng]
    AI[app/ai/*<br/>ML / RAG — XGBoost, LangChain]

    A -->|depends on| S
    S -->|depends on| M
    AI -->|depends on| S
    AI -->|depends on| M
    A -.->|❌ KHÔNG được| AI

    style A fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#0052a3
    style S fill:#e0e7ff,stroke:#003e80
    style M fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706
    style AI fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a
```

> **Rule cứng:** AI/chatbot **KHÔNG** được import từ `app.api.v1.*` để tránh circular import + giữ AI testable độc lập.
> Logic dùng chung (vd "highest GPA wins") nằm ở `services/grade_aggregator.py` — single source of truth.

---

# Database Schema (10 bảng)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    users ||--o| students : "1-1"
    users ||--o{ events : "created_by"
    students ||--o{ enrollments : ""
    students ||--o{ warnings : ""
    students ||--o{ predictions : ""
    students ||--o{ notifications : ""
    students ||--o{ chat_messages : ""
    courses ||--o{ enrollments : ""
    warnings ||--o| notifications : "FK link"
    documents ||--|| documents : "vector chunks"

    users { uuid id PK; varchar email UK; enum role; bool is_active }
    students { uuid id PK; varchar mssv UK; varchar full_name; varchar faculty; int cohort; float gpa_cumulative; int warning_level }
    courses { uuid id PK; varchar course_code; varchar name; int credits }
    enrollments { uuid id PK; varchar semester; float midterm_score; float final_score; float total_score; varchar grade_letter; enum status; bool is_finalized }
    warnings { uuid id PK; int level; varchar semester; text reason; float gpa_at_warning; float ai_risk_score; bool is_resolved; enum created_by }
    predictions { uuid id PK; varchar semester; float risk_score; enum risk_level; jsonb risk_factors; jsonb predicted_courses }
    notifications { uuid id PK; enum type; varchar title; text content; bool is_read; timestamp email_sent_at }
    events { uuid id PK; varchar title; enum event_type; enum target_audience; timestamp start_time; bool is_mandatory }
    documents { uuid id PK; text content; vector embedding; varchar source_file; int chunk_index; bool is_active }
    chat_messages { uuid id PK; enum role; text content; jsonb citations }
```

